text: The Parkshore is a 556ft (169m) tall skyscraper in Chicago, Illinois. It was completed in 1991 and has 56 floors. Barancik Conte designed the building. The Parkshore is the 53rd tallest in Chicago. ==Related pages== *List of tallest buildings in Chicago ==Other websites== Category:Skyscrapers in Chicago Category:1991 establishments in Illinois
title: The Parkshore
